{"id":213,"date":"2025-09-17T07:17:43","date_gmt":"2025-09-17T07:17:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/?page_id=213"},"modified":"2026-03-14T04:54:21","modified_gmt":"2026-03-14T04:54:21","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<section class=\"wp-block-app-block-section-about-banner section-about-banner undefined\"><div class=\"t-cr-wrapper\"><div class=\"t-cr\"><div class=\"t-box title-intro\"><div class=\"hg-1-wrapper\"><h1 class=\"hg-1\">About Jasmine<\/h1><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box media-intro-wrapper\" data-parallax=\"20\" data-parallax-target=\".media-outer\" data-parallax-no-clip=\"true\" data-parallax-no-scale=\"true\" data-parallax-bounds-start=\"0\" data-parallax-end=\"bottom+=50% top\"><div class=\"media-intro\"><div class=\"media-outer\"><div class=\"media-caption-container-wrapper\"><div class=\"media-caption-container\"><div class=\"media-caption media-caption--left\"><div class=\"media-caption-inner \">WHO&#8217;S THIS?<\/div><\/div><div class=\"media-caption media-caption--right\"><div class=\"media-caption-inner\">HELLO, HI, HEY<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"media-wrapper\"><picture class=\"t-ma\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/jas_website_image-scaled.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/jas_website_image-scaled.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><\/div><div class=\"media-social-container-wrapper\"><div class=\"media-social-container\"><a class=\"media-social btn-cta \" href=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/JasmineGunarto_resume_MD.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"btn-cta-inner\"><span class=\"btn-cta-text\">RESUME<\/span><\/div><\/a><a class=\"media-social btn-cta \" href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/jas-gunarto\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><div class=\"btn-cta-inner\"><span class=\"btn-cta-text\">LINKEDIN<\/span><\/div><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box section-body\"><div class=\"body-caption-container\"><div class=\"body-caption body-caption-1\">ADVOCATE OF<br>TYPE \ud83d\ude42<\/div><div class=\"body-caption body-caption-2\">FUNNY?, KIND,<br>A HUMAN BEING<\/div><div class=\"body-caption body-caption-3\">SNACK + FOOD<br>GIVER<\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-body\">Heya, I\u2019m Jas, a multidisciplinary designer from Jakarta, Indonesia, now in the US, working across graphic, motion, and brand. <br><br>I love mixed media, storytelling, and letting good conversations and everyday moments sneak into my work.<br><br>When I\u2019m not designing, I\u2019m usually watching films, traveling (when i can), or hunting for good food.<br><br>Feel free to chat with me through my email and let\u2019s even talk about food \ud83c\udf5c:<br><a href=\"mailto:jasminegunarto1@gmail.com\">jasminegunarto1@gmail.com<\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"wp-block-app-block-section-row-gallery section-row-gallery\"><div class=\"t-cr\"><div class=\"t-box t-box-c\"><div class=\"container-media\"><div class=\"item-media\"><div class=\"media-image-wrapper\"><picture class=\"media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/favicon-1.5.png\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/favicon-1.5.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><\/div><\/div><div class=\"item-media\"><div class=\"media-image-wrapper\"><picture class=\"media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/favicon-2.png\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/favicon-2.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><\/div><\/div><div class=\"item-media\"><div class=\"media-image-wrapper\">